ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Damn hard class -- don't take it if you have a busy semester ahead. But you do get a lot back from it.
Difficult, fast-paced, but enjoyable and worth it.
I would definitely recommend the course to other students. It is such a great way to get acquainted with neuroimaging methods and analysis.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I feel like I can somewhat defend myself in the methods necessary (with further guidance, of course). The course is highly significant for my methodologies employed in my research.
